based on mozille firefox core.

runs like this:
su -l puppy -c 'fox-based-browser -profile "/mnt/sda1/myprofilefolder" \$1'


Prefs are defined like this : 
user_pref("browser.download.dir", "/mnt/sda1/downloads_linux");
user_pref("browser.download.folderList", 2);
user_pref("browser.cache.disk.parent_directory", "/mnt/sda1/downloads_linux/.cache/cyberfox");